      garlic 3 cloves
      olive-oil 2 tbsp
      parmesan 50 g OR nutritional-yeast 30 g
      basil 10 g
      salt 1 tsp

    STEPS:
      boil-water: bring water to boil FOR 10 min
      cook-pasta: add pasta to boiling water FOR 12 min AFTER boil-water
      saute: heat olive-oil and garlic FOR 3 min
      simmer-sauce: add tomatoes and simmer FOR 20 min AFTER saute
      NOTE: cook-pasta and simmer-sauce run in parallel — no dependency between them
      drain: drain pasta FOR 1 min AFTER cook-pasta
      combine: toss pasta with sauce FOR 2 min AFTER drain
      garnish: add parmesan and basil FOR 1 min AFTER combine
  "

-- SPAWNED CELL: example-2 (v3)
⊢ example-2
