      IF-SUB tofu: press tofu between towels FOR 15 min ALONGSIDE rice
      prep-veg: chop broccoli and bell pepper FOR 8 min ALONGSIDE rice
      NOTE: rice, tofu-press, and prep-veg all run in parallel
      heat-wok: heat wok with vegetable-oil FOR 2 min STARTS-WHEN rice HAS 5 min LEFT
      cook-protein: stir-fry chicken or tofu FOR 5 min AFTER heat-wok
      stir-fry-veg: add vegetables and stir-fry FOR 4 min AFTER cook-protein
      sauce: add soy-sauce ginger garlic FOR 2 min AFTER stir-fry-veg
      finish: drizzle sesame-oil and serve with rice FOR 1 min AFTER sauce
